{"tid":795442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[厲害了] 小米雷軍99億人民幣薪酬創世界紀錄，相當於100個Tim Cook","createTime":"2018-08-27T04:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T10:30:31.000Z","uid":31744,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"205cd28ed3f07b9cc5a203a3dd765ab4c8b3eedd","tid":795442,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/122952_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F122952_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg&h=7b1da730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月22日，小米公司公佈了上市後首份財報，有兩件事情讓外界大感驚奇，一是小米終於繳出&ldquo;轉虧為盈&rdquo;的獲利成績，另外就是雷軍的天價薪酬！小米財報顯示，今年第二季營收為452億元人民幣，比去年同期增長68.3%，今年第二季盈餘則為146億人民幣。而按非國際財務報告準則，小米今年第二季盈餘比去年同期增長25.1%，至21億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雷軍薪酬造成行政支出暴增44.7倍</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小米今年第二季銷售成本從去年同期的230億人民幣增加到今年第二季的396億人民幣，增加71.9%，行政開支也從去年同期的2億2千萬人民幣增加至今年第二季的100億人民幣，增加44.7倍，行政開支暴增，主要來自雷軍的薪酬。透過比對小米招股書可以發現，今年第二季財報，是因為一次性的給小米董事長雷軍以股份為基礎的薪酬99億人民幣，才造成行政支出暴增。全球市值最高的蘋果公司總裁庫克年薪加獎金也才1280萬美元，雷軍的工資相當於100個庫克了！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/123015_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F123015_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=195e26fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雷軍這個薪酬也刷新了全球上市公司高管領薪酬的紀錄。</span><br />\n<br />\n小米CFO周受資表示，小米第二季行政費用包含了99億元上市前股權激勵的開支，&ldquo;這是一次性的開支，所以在調整後，21億的淨利潤是很健康的。本質上，二季度調整後利潤還是很健康的水準。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n此前6月23日，小米在香港四季酒店召開全球發售新聞發佈會，會上有媒體問及雷軍在小米公開招股書前獲得的超90億元人民幣的股權激勵可能會給小米上市所帶來的盈利風險。<br />\n<br />\n對此，小米總裁林斌回應稱，董事會對董事長/CEO在上市前的股權激勵，在過去很多全球新經濟公司上市時都是慣例，小米不是第一家，也不是最後一家。林斌表示，小米這次股權激勵是在雷軍完全不知情的前提下，幾個董事開會，大家一致贊成通過做出的決定。&ldquo;這也是大家對雷總過去8年帶著團隊把小米做到這個規模，同時也是對中國製造業做的事情的肯定。我們都覺得這是實至名歸。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n本文綜合自小米財報、信傳媒、小米官網、新京報、騰訊財經報導"},{"pid":"a623572a38ef4710fe54665a5f6fea0bbfe2cc32","tid":795442,"uid":43842,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"唔怪得小米升唔上30蚊"},{"pid":"a43749045a07264124af8327642a6711e196a04e","tid":795442,"uid":31744,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a623572a38ef4710fe54665a5f6fea0bbfe2cc32","tid":795442,"uid":43842,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"唔怪得小米升唔上30蚊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"港豬買小米進貢雷軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e721fd15196021b321999f4d54ec4ae58f3963","tid":795442,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"同股唔同權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e0ff07f83303654f9568576b3ce57d6996d94","tid":795442,"uid":126731,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:37:40.000Z","msg":"人地外國CEO就收股票當糧, 打工推股價做. 支那爛米就調轉, 同股不同權, 放晒D股票, 集資幫自己出糧. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67d5642bd47fec5be9c47ddb9361005c4b23b4b","tid":795442,"uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"上市集資出佢出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148ce7d7ca69d710b7dee1eaaa5d741648828866","tid":795442,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook最抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbb2dc25e1d8a8b70b4a5777d1c6b7f155bb2a4","tid":795442,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"交幾錢稅?"},{"pid":"b15219d35607d36aba11850d78732226de0fa6bd","tid":795442,"uid":44358,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"成間公司當係佢私人俱樂部<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貪都唔好咁狼死呀，食相咁核突，間野賺一蚊，佢就食一蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67be472d45316588369b71297e03a210798497d3","tid":795442,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"雷軍人工  = 馬化騰 x Tim Cook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b042f446faa637308ef5c5485e4fec805558f5","tid":795442,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"集資交稅俾黨"},{"pid":"39adb8798f8a7678a37f157879aee4ba6e49f140","tid":795442,"uid":31744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"我哋麵神啲$$去哂雷軍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2337b21748f12a083f8c63706784b15ea94f198b","tid":795442,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"打佢間公司工=slave<br />\n<br />\n(佢食剩才俾你）"},{"pid":"4c329b113539e2b8cfe75a563982f765032fc882","tid":795442,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148ce7d7ca69d710b7dee1eaaa5d741648828866","tid":795442,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook最抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"咪又係迫你UPDATE IOS, 迫你買新機<br />\n整D爛MON賺維修費"},{"pid":"87e203685f4fbbfa5746af0e28e7c00b7abc9d30","tid":795442,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c329b113539e2b8cfe75a563982f765032fc882","tid":795442,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148ce7d7ca69d710b7dee1eaaa5d741648828866","tid":795442,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook最抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20